Hotel used as quarantine place for suspected cases of coronavirus collapses in China. A five-story hotel collapsed this Saturday in Quanzhou, China. According to Chinese media, at least 70 people are arrested among the debris. To date were rescued 23, refers to the Daily China newspaper.
We collapsed around 7:00 pm (11h00 from Lisbon) on Saturday.




